The paper deals with communication schemes in a cellular system with multiple transmit antennas and single receiver antennas, which falls under the category of information theory (cs.IT). The paper also discusses the design of robust broadcasting schemes, which involves optimization and control aspects, making it relevant to the sub-categories of networked systems (cs.NI) and systems and control (cs.SY). The paper also mentions the use of computationally-efficient design formulations, which could be relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
